Drago and Tretorous: With his back against the wall, Dan tries flipping the script on Haavik by challenging him to a game of his own - a Bakugan Brawl. If Dan wins, then Haavik will have to set him, and the other Awesome Brawler's free.

And to make things worse, he doesn't have his collar with Baku-balls. At the compound where he's being held, he runs into an old foe.  It's up to these two enemies to team up and escape their captor.

When he attempts to break into a museum to return artifacts, his mentor Storm is waiting for him. A Bakugan brawl breaks out between two when Storm rolls out his new Bakugan: Cimoga.

The intensity ramps up when Pepe, his teammates and a mysterious coach show up for a little fun. It will take major teamwork for the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan to defeat this rowdy bunch.
